    "excerpt": "<p>This is a sticky post. There are a few things to verify: The sticky post should be distinctly\u00a0recognizable\u00a0in some way in comparison to normal posts. You can style the .sticky class if you are using the post_class() function to generate your post classes, which is a best practice. They should show at the very top [&hellip;]<\/p>\n",
